title: Recession Fears, Hong Kong Protests, 2020
itunes:title: Recession Fears, Hong Kong Protests, 2020
description:
Guests include: Sean Rankin, Executive Director of the Democratic Attorneys General Association and Chris Prudhome, Republican Strategist and President, Vote America Now.

Brett Bruen, President of the Global Situation Room and former White House Director of Global Engagement discussed the Hong Kong protests.
